#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:1
msgid "Shell API"
msgstr "Shell API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:3
msgid "Shell parsing helpers are available under `ptool.sh` and `p.sh`."
msgstr "Shell 解析辅助能力位于 `ptool.sh` 和 `p.sh` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:5
msgid "These helpers work at the shell-word level. They are intended for splitting, quoting, and joining argument strings using POSIX shell-style rules, not for parsing full shell syntax such as pipelines, redirections, command substitution, or variable expansion."
msgstr "这些辅助能力工作在 shell word 这一层级。它们用于按照 POSIX shell 风格规则拆分、引用和拼接参数字符串，而不是用于解析完整的 shell 语法，例如管道、重定向、命令替换或变量展开。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:10
msgid "ptool.sh.split"
msgstr "ptool.sh.split"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:12
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:14
msgid "`ptool.sh.split(command)` parses a command string using shell-style rules and returns an argument array."
msgstr "`ptool.sh.split(command)` 使用 shell 风格规则解析命令字符串，并返回参数数组。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:17
msgid "`command` (string, required): The command string to split."
msgstr "`command`（string，必填）：要拆分的命令字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:18
msgid "Returns: `string[]`."
msgstr "返回：`string[]`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:20
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:20"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:22
msgid "This parses shell words only. It does not interpret shell operators or execute expansions."
msgstr "这里只解析 shell words。本 API 不会解释 shell 操作符，也不会执行展开。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:25
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:25"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:31
msgid "The `args` above is equivalent to:"
msgstr "上面的 `args` 等价于："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:37
msgid "ptool.sh.quote"
msgstr "ptool.sh.quote"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:39
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:39"
msgid "`Unreleased` - Introduced."
msgstr "`Unreleased` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:41
msgid "`ptool.sh.quote(word)` quotes a single shell word so it can be embedded safely into a shell command string."
msgstr "`ptool.sh.quote(word)` 会对单个 shell word 进行引用，使其可以安全地嵌入到 shell 命令字符串中。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:44
msgid "`word` (string, required): The shell word to quote."
msgstr "`word`（string，必填）：要引用的 shell word。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:45
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:45"
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "返回：`string`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:47
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:47"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:49
msgid "The returned string is shell-safe and semantically equivalent to the input word."
msgstr "返回的字符串对 shell 是安全的，并且在语义上等价于输入的 word。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:51
msgid "This preserves shell-word meaning, not the original textual spelling."
msgstr "这里保留的是 shell word 的语义，而不是原始文本的书写形式。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:53
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:53"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:60
msgid "ptool.sh.join"
msgstr "ptool.sh.join"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:62
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:62"
msgid "`Unreleased` - Introduced."
msgstr "`Unreleased` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:64
msgid "`ptool.sh.join(words)` joins an argument array into a shell command string, quoting words when needed."
msgstr "`ptool.sh.join(words)` 会把参数数组拼成一个 shell 命令字符串，并在需要时对其中的 word 进行引用。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:67
msgid "`words` (string[], required): The shell words to join."
msgstr "`words`（string[]，必填）：要拼接的 shell words。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:68
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:68"
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "返回：`string`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:70
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:70"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:72
msgid "Consecutive words are joined with a single space."
msgstr "相邻 words 会使用单个空格连接。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:73
msgid "The output is suitable for passing to a POSIX-style shell."
msgstr "输出结果适合传递给 POSIX 风格的 shell。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:74
msgid "This aims for shell-word round-tripping, so `ptool.sh.split(ptool.sh.join(words))` is equivalent to `words`."
msgstr "这里追求 shell word 级别的往返一致性，因此 `ptool.sh.split(ptool.sh.join(words))` 与 `words` 等价。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:76
msgid "`ptool.sh.join(ptool.sh.split(command))` may normalize quoting and spacing instead of preserving the original command text."
msgstr "`ptool.sh.join(ptool.sh.split(command))` 可能会规范化引用方式和空格，而不是保留原始命令文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/sh.md:79
